Xatkit 2.0.0-SNAPSHOT API

Core 
Package Description
com.xatkit.core
Contains the core components of the Xatkit framework.
com.xatkit.core.interpreter  
com.xatkit.core.interpreter.operation  
com.xatkit.core.interpreter.operation.object  
com.xatkit.core.platform
Contains the abstract classes to implement to provide custom platforms.
com.xatkit.core.platform.action
Contains the abstract classes to implement to provide custom platform's actions.
com.xatkit.core.platform.io
Contains the abstract classes to implement to provide custom platform's input provider.
com.xatkit.core.recognition
Contains the abstract classes to implement to provide custom intent recognition.
com.xatkit.core.recognition.dialogflow
An intent recognition implementation for the DialogFlow platform.
com.xatkit.core.server
Contains the Xatkit server implementation.
com.xatkit.core.session
Contains the classes to manage sessions and contexts.
Plugins 
Package Description
com.xatkit.plugins
Contains the Xatkit plugins bundled with the standard Xatkit distribution.
com.xatkit.plugins.core
The root package of the Xatkit Core plugin.
com.xatkit.plugins.core.platform
Contains the platform implementation of the Xatkit Core plugin.
com.xatkit.plugins.core.platform.action
Contains the action implementations available in the Xatkit Core platform.
com.xatkit.plugins.discord
The root package of the Xatkit Discord plugin.
com.xatkit.plugins.discord.platform
Contains the platform implementation of the Xatkit Discord plugin.
com.xatkit.plugins.discord.platform.action
Contains the action implementations available in the Xatkit Discord platform.
com.xatkit.plugins.discord.platform.io
Contains the intent and event providers available in the Xatkit Discord platform.
com.xatkit.plugins.github
The root package of the Xatkit Github plugin.
com.xatkit.plugins.github.platform
Contains the platform implementation of the Xatkit Github plugin.
com.xatkit.plugins.github.platform.action
Contains the action implementations available in the Xatkit Github platform.
com.xatkit.plugins.github.platform.io
Contains the intent and event providers available in the Xatkit Github platform.
com.xatkit.plugins.log
The root package of the Xatkit Log plugin.
com.xatkit.plugins.log.platform
Contains the platform implementation of the Xatkit Log plugin.
com.xatkit.plugins.log.platform.action
Contains the action implementations available in the Xatkit Log platform.
com.xatkit.plugins.slack
The root package of the Xatkit Slack plugin.
com.xatkit.plugins.slack.platform
Contains the platform implementation of the Xatkit Slack plugin.
com.xatkit.plugins.slack.platform.action
Contains the action implementations available in the Xatkit Slack platform.
com.xatkit.plugins.slack.platform.io
Contains the intent and event providers available in the Xatkit Slack platform.
Models 
Package Description
com.xatkit.execution
Contains the interfaces to manipulate Execution models.
com.xatkit.execution.impl
Contains the implementation classes used to manipulate Execution models.
com.xatkit.execution.util
Contains utility classes used to manipulate Execution models.
com.xatkit.intent
Contains the interfaces to manipulate Intent models.
com.xatkit.intent.impl
Contains the implementation classes used to manipulate Intent models.
com.xatkit.intent.util
Contains utility classes used to manipulate Intent models.
com.xatkit.platform
Contains the interfaces to manipulate Platform models.
com.xatkit.platform.impl
Contains the implementation classes used to manipulate Platform models.
com.xatkit.platform.util
Contains utility classes used to manipulate Platform models.
Other Packages 
Package Description
com.xatkit
Xatkit base package.
com.xatkit.common
Contains the interfaces to manipulate Common models.
com.xatkit.common.impl
Contains the implementation classes used to manipulate Common models.
com.xatkit.common.util
Contains utility classes used to manipulate Common models.
com.xatkit.core_resources.utils
Utility classes to load/save platforms and libraries in a platform-independent way.
com.xatkit.util
Utility classes that are used by the Xatkit framework.
